Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置在旧校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最深处的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把夕子学姐交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在里面对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把门打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐是？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是发什么神经啊 这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家冷静 为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐就在里面对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把夕子学姐藏起来了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没法跟他们沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快点逃走 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把夕子学姐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新谷同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把夕子学姐交出来..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有人都会被杀掉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 贞一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夕子学姐干的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从窗口跑出来绕到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 夕子学姐没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真可惜 还差一点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没做过自我介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做桐岛有子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个学校 夕子这个名字代表着什么样的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.73,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(445.667,610)}有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 讨厌迷信怪谈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌散布怪谈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有..我最讨厌你们这样没事找事的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么事比把你们统统摧毁更加令人愉快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的骚动 是你设计的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐什么的消失了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死怪谈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那孩子也是“夕子”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶~ 好可怕~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子！这孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为害怕怪谈中的夕子学姐而很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想同为“夕子”的你应该会知道点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了我不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪谈!？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真相信有这事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子都出问题了吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也 也是呢......
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪什么的 不可能真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是害怕的东西还是会害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也都是这么想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(235,160)\fad(300,300)}回你的旧校舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,480)\fad(300,300)}快点成佛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(875,540)\fad(300,300)}别来学校了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.66,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1105,180)\fad(300,300)}消失吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了它..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪谈什么的..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你们..无论是怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是相信怪谈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家..全都..全都！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有子 怎么办啊 有子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到夕子学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被红人杀掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 红人要杀的是夕子学姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
